CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 7, 1956, pg. 17 reads: "...5. Mrs. Isabel Stewart and Miss Clara Williams, extreme back center, served the crowd refreshing Coca-Cola...Harris Photos"
TitMainTitle: Crowd of people in front of Isabel Stewart and Clara Williams in Coca-Cola booth, in Syria Mosque for the 1956 Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair
